quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Kodi Ife sitidatsegule chifuwa chako
  94,2,Ndi kukuchotsa katundu wako wolemera
  94,3,Amene amalemetsa msana wako
  94,4,Ndipo tidakweza mbiri yako yabwino
  94,5,Ndithudi m’mavuto muli chithandizo
  94,6,Ndithudi m’mavuto muli chithandizo
  94,7,"Ndipo pamene wamaliza, pembedza Mulungu"
  94,8,Ndipo dzipereke kwathunthu kwa Ambuye wako
  95,1,Pali mtengo wa mkuyu ndi mtengo wa azitona
  95,2,Ndi pali phiri la Sinai
  95,3,Ndi pali Mzinda uwu wa mtendere
  95,4,Ndithudi Ife tidamulenga munthu m’chikombole chabwino
  95,5,Ndipo tinamutsitsa kukhala wapansi zedi
  95,6,"Kupatula amene amakhulupirira ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino, iwo adzalandira mphotho yosatha"
  95,7,"Kodi ndi chiyani, chimene chili kukupangitsani kukana tsiku la chiweruzo"
  95,8,Kodi Mulungu si woweruza wabwino kuposa oweruza onse
  96,1,Werenga! M’dzina la Ambuye wako amene analenga
  96,2,Yemwe adalenga munthu kuchokera ku kadontho kamagazi oundana
  96,3,werenga! Ndipo Ambuye wako ndiye wopereka mowoolowa manja
  96,4,Amene anaphunzitsa ndi cholembera
  96,5,Anaphunzitsa munthu chimene sanali kuchidziwa
  96,6,"Iyayi! Ndithudi, munthu amalakwa mopyola muyeso"
  96,7,Chifukwa amaganiza kuti iye ndi oima payekha
  96,8,Ndithudi! Nonse mudzabwerera kwa Ambuye wanu
  96,9,Kodi mwamuona munthu amene amaletsa
  96,10,Kapolo pamene akupemphera
  96,11,Kodi mwamuona ngati iye alikutsatira chilangizo chabwino
  96,12,Kapena kulamulira machitidwe abwino
  96,13,Ndiuze ngati iye akana choonadi ndipo salabadira
  96,14,Kodi iye sadziwa kuti Mulungu amaona zinthu zonse
  96,15,"Iyayi! Ngati iye sasiya, Ife tidzamududuluza pogwira tsitsi la pa mphumi pake"
  96,16,Mphumi yabodza ndi yochimwa
  96,17,Ndipo mulekeni iye aitane anzake oti amuthandize
  96,18,Ife tidzaitana osunga Gahena
  96,19,Iyayi! Usamumvere iye. Gunditsa mphumi yako pansi ndipo idza pafupi ndi Mulungu
  97,1,Ndithudi tinavumbulutsa ilo mu usiku wamphamvu
  97,2,Kodi ndi chiyani chimene chingakuuzeni kuti mudziwe kuti usiku wamphamvu ndi otani
  97,3,Usiku wamphamvu ndi wabwino kuposa miyezi chikwi chimodzi
  97,4,"Mu usiku umenewu Angelo ndi Mzimu, ndi chilolezo cha Mulungu, amachoka kumwamba ndi kutsika pansi ndi malamulo ake onse"
  97,5,Mtendere mpaka m’mbandakucha
  98,1,"Iwo amene sakhulupirira a m’gulu la anthu a m’Buku ndi anthu opembedza mafano, sadzasiya kusakhulupilira mpaka pamene zizindikiro zooneka zitaperekedwa kwa iwo"
  98,2,Mtumwi wochokera kwa Mulungu amene ali kuwerenga kuchokera pa Masamba oyera
  98,3,Amene ali ndi malamulo angwiro ndi omveka bwino ochokera kwa Mulungu
  98,4,Ndipo anthu okhulupirira Buku sanayambe kugawikana pakati pawo mpaka pamene zizindikiro zooneka zidaperekedwa kwa iwo
  98,5,"Ndipo Al-Zalzala\t659 iwo sadalamulidwe koma kuti azipembedza Mulungu ndipo kuti asapembedze wina aliyense koma Iye yekha ndipo kuti adzipemphera pa nthawi yake ndi kupereka msonkho wothandiza anthu osauka. Ndipo chimenechi ndicho chipembedzo chabwino"
  98,6,"Ndithudi iwo amene sakhulupirira amene ali pakati pa anthu a m’Buku, ndi anthu opembedza mafano, adzakhala ku moto wa ku Gahena. Iwo ndiwo oipa zedi pa zolengedwa zonse"
  98,7,Ndithudi iwo amene atsatira chikhulupiriro choonadi ndipo amachita ntchito zabwino ndiwo olemekezeka pa zolengedwa zonse
  98,8,"Mphotho yawo imene ili ndi Ambuye wawo ndi kuwaika m’minda imene imathiriridwa ndi madzi ya m’mitsinje pansi pake, kumene adzakhalako nthawi zonse. Mulungu ndi wosangalala ndi iwo ndipo nawonso ndi osangalala ndi Iye. M’menemo ndi m’mene munthu oopa Mulungu adzalandirire mphotho yake"
  99,1,Pamene dziko lidzagwedezeka ndi chivomerezi chomaliza
  99,2,Ndipo pamene nthaka idzatulutsa katundu amene ali m’kati mwake
  99,3,"Ndipo munthu adzafunsa: “Kodi yatani?”"
  99,4,Pa tsikuli nthaka idzaulula zonse
  99,5,Chifukwa Ambuye wako wayiuza kuti itero
  99,6,Pa tsikuli mtundu wa anthu udzadza m’magulu osiyana siyana kudzalangizidwa ntchito zawo
  99,7,"Motero aliyense amene amachita chabwino cholemera ngati njere ya mpiru, adzachiona"
  99,8,"Ndipo aliyense amene amachita choipa cholemera ngati njere ya mpiru, adzachiona"
  100,1,Palizothamangakwambirindikupumakwawokofulumira
  100,2,Ndi zimene zimaonetsa moto zikamathamanga
  100,3,Ndipo zimachita nkhondo m’mbandakucha
  100,4,Ndi kuonetsa fumbi
  100,5,Ndi kuphwanya pakati gulu la adani
  100,6,Ndithudi! Munthu sathokoza kwaAmbuye wake
  100,7,Ndipo mwini wake amachitira umboni zimenezi
  100,8,Ndithudi iye ali kukonda chuma kwambiri